data.description: THIS IS A MUST SEE!!! Check out this beautifully maintained home featuring 3 beds/ 2 baths/ boosting 2000 square feet under air and a 2 car garage with a gorgeous POOL. Home features cathedral ceilings, open floor concept, split bedrooms and much more. The kitchen is spacious with granite counter tops, custom cabinets with soft close doors & draws, stainless steel appliances, island bar features extra cabinets, closet pantry, recessed lighting, and eating space in kitchen with an open concept to living room perfect for entertaining YOUR guest. Separate dining room and BONUS room that you can use for an office or den. Inside laundry room. Master bedroom is oversized with a walk in closet. Master bathroom with separate shower and garden tub for relaxing! Updates include: Roof "2019", IMPACT WINDOWS "2020", AC "2018" and Hot Water Heater "2020". YOU will feel like your at YOUR own private resort with the gorgeous L-shaped pool with a waterfall feature and spacious lanai for you and your guest! Nicely landscaped and fenced in yard so bring your furry friends. No HOA or deed restrictions!! This home is conveniently located in a nice neighborhood but close to restaurants, shopping, beaches and much more!!! Ask to see this one first...make YOUR appointment today!!!
